"aggregation operator and :dbcommand:`geoNear` command that enables users "
"to specify which geospatial index to use when querying a collection with "
"multiple geospatial indexes. Previously, to use the :pipeline:`$geoNear` "
"aggregation operator or :dbcommand:`geoNear` command, the collection "
"could only have one geospatial index."
